{"tid":1064932,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Endgame睇唔睇3D imax好","createTime":"2019-03-17T02:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T16:36:07.000Z","uid":60171,"like":46,"dislike":92,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"27ad852cd6d7a974b6c30afbd0389a08071ce074","tid":1064932,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"本身唔係太好3D嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且今次仲要睇3個鐘以上其實會唔會睇完好攰頭暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但作為marvel fans仲要係Chris同Robert告別作<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n元朗睇3D imax早場好似幾抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以諗緊下個月上映好唔好睇3D imax<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如無意外都會3刷，iw都係睇左3次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />3D imax<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />2D算啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次iw有睇3D imax嘅巴絲打可以講下感受點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b8f244d9a46ad14eba54d3fca5e03ff135e19a","tid":1064932,"uid":619,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"上次喺元朗坐最邊睇完iw暈咗大半個鐘浪，但今次應該都照睇imax<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a1d0f4fbd92280dfe36ae3f3624423d18fca0f","tid":1064932,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T02:06:33.000Z","msg":"咁快就4個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkg